headline: How Recent Developments Are Rewriting the Story for Eaton
summary: Eaton’s stock narrative has shifted as the consensus analyst price target recently edged higher from $404.21 to $410.70. This signals growing optimism among market watchers. The change reflects analyst confidence driven largely by robust data center order growth and the anticipated benefits from the Boyd Thermal acquisition.
